reviews.reviewtitle: Preface of this book shows its intention
reviews.reviewbody:
The compiler of this book, Mr. Robert Christy, in his preface is
claiming that the verse in Hitopadesha is the most atrocious statement against women. He, as all the past and present western interpreters with hidden agendas against the great Bharatheeya Dharma, kept on distorting the essence of many such slokas without taking effort to interpret the former and later  portions of the same. It's true that a lot of cunning authors could inject poison to the Indian minds in this way for the past many decades. But this is not going work out anymore as Indians are on the path of self-realization.
